# CAS host-suite XFAIL list (CAS-01). Consumed by tests/host/cas_suite_main.cpp.
# Format: SUITE<TAB>KIND<TAB>match-substring<TAB>ticket/reason
#   KIND = case    -> substring matched against per-case [FAIL]/FAIL: log lines
#   KIND = crash   -> substring matched against the crash signal name (SIGSEGV, ...)
#   KIND = timeout -> suite exceeded the 60 s per-suite timeout
# An entry that stops failing turns XPASS and FAILS the run — prune it in the
# same PR that fixes the underlying issue. Initial inventory:
# docs/specs/NUMOS_CAS_CAS01_CAS02_EXECUTION_PLAN.md §H.
